lternatives</h2> <!--[PREMOD7]--><span class=3D"marker PREMOD7 mod-inline">=
</span><p class=3D"topic-paragraph">The Caesar cipher allows only 25 differ=
ent encryptions when using plain text. A brute force method can hence be us=
ed to decipher the message, using all 25 possible shifts and then selecting=
